Have any of you ever seen the movie "End of Days"?  It's the weirdest, creepiest thing I've ever seen.

There is one particular scene where Gabriel Byrne walks into a guys house, and asks the man about the two women: "This your daughter?  This your mother?"  Then, the scene immediately cuts to Gabriel Byrne having sex with the mother while the daughter lays next to them and masturbates.  Then the two women make out and Gabriel Byrne, still humping the mom, uses his devil powers to make the limbs of the women fuse together weirdly.  Who the fuck made up this scene?  It's not cool or funny even in an ironic campy way.  Ugh.
